<Algorithm code="           1. Perform ? RequireInternalSlot(_O_, [[TypedArrayName]]).           1. Assert: _O_ has a [[ViewedArrayBuffer]] internal slot.           1. Let _taRecord_ be MakeTypedArrayWithBufferWitnessRecord(_O_, _order_).           1. If IsTypedArrayOutOfBounds(_taRecord_) is *true*, throw a *TypeError* exception.           1. Return _taRecord_.         ">
